data.description: Pinnacle at Wood Ranch presents an exclusive collection of luxury townhomes nestled in Simi Valley. Situated within the esteemed Wood Ranch master-planned community, this residence claims an enviable position of a hilltop, granting residents breathtaking panoramic views of the surrounding landscape.The homes at Pinnacle at Wood Ranch showcase remarkable and meticulously crafted exterior elevations, exuding inspiration and attention to detail. Inside, the residences feature gourmet kitchens equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, ensuring a high-end culinary experience. The open floor plans foster a sense of spaciousness and facilitate seamless transitions.This particular home within the enclave offers three generously sized bedrooms, accompanied by two and a half elegant baths. With approximately 1,996 square feet of meticulously designed living space, there is ample room for comfortable and sophisticated living. Pinnacle at Wood Ranch have the privilege of enjoying a private swim club, a true oasis for relaxation and recreation. The swim club includes a sparkling swimming pool, a rejuvenating spa, and convenient restroom facilities, all exclusively accessible to the community's residents.Convenience is another hallmark of this new community, with its strategic location near shopping and dining options. Whether you seek retail therapy or desire culinary delights, the close proximity to various establishments caters to a diverse range of preferences.
